Rancho_Cordova.Carmichael Park: Carmichael Park is a major 38-acre (150,000 m2) park in Carmichael, California, an unincorporated suburb of Sacramento, California. The park includes 5 ballfields and 6 tennis courts. The Community Clubhouse, Veterans' Memorial Building, the Daniel Bishop Memorial Pavilion for the Performing Arts, and the Great Wall of Carmichael are all located within the park.
